title: Printer's Sample Book (USA), 1877–78
creditline: Gift of Frederick J. Whitehead from the collection compiled by his father Cornelius Whitehead at the Pacific Print Works of Lawrence, Massachusetts
description: Small notebook with handwritten formulas for dyestuffs used for printed textiles. Contains 157 samples in various designs.

tombstone.epitaph: Printer's Sample Book (USA), 1877–78; Manufactured by Old Pacific Print Works ; leather, paper, cotton; Gift of Frederick J. Whitehead from the collection compiled by his father Cornelius Whitehead at the Pacific Print Works of Lawrence, Massachusetts; 1945-55-37
